content:
Alter Product Attribute Values Through Slider Controls

This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions. Show attributes of the currency, number, and percent data types as sliders at run time. Instead of typing in a number, or using increment buttons, drag the slider on a predefined scale to adjust the attribute values. Sliders are intuitive and provide immediate visual feedback as your users make attribute adjustments.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions.
